							Hasbro receives a large number of requests for use of Hasbro’s intellectual property and trademarks. If you wish to submit a Permission to Use Request, please fill out
							this form
							and return via email to
							permissions@hasbro.com. Permission to Use Requests typically take 1-2 weeks to process, however some requests can take up to 4 weeks. If you do not hear from a Hasbro representative within 4 weeks of submission, we unfortunately are unable to approve your request. While we do review each submission, due to the volume of requests, we are simply unable to respond to every inquiry. Permission to Use is not granted without express consent from Hasbro.
							
